shows.
Compared with last month, the poll puts Labour on 46 per cent (up 1 per
cent, and up 7 per cent on its general election performance), the SNP on 25
(up 2, up 4), the Tories at 16 (no change, down 10) and the Liberal
Democrats at 12 (down 4, down 1).
