<HEADLINE>
FT  02 JUL 93 / Eco-labelling scheme launched
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE European Community's long-delayed eco-labelling scheme was launched
yesterday for washing machines and dishwashers.
The scheme will award labels to products which satisfy environmental
criteria devised in Brussels, and is intended to help consumers identify
products which are least harmful to the environment. It relies on
manufacturers voluntarily submitting their products to be assessed.
