FT  01 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Losses halved at Seafield
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
HALVED pre-tax losses of Pounds 11.1m, compared with Pounds 22.4m, were
announced by Seafield, the Dublin-based transport, warehousing and property
group, for 1992.
