and over the past three months the group had been involved in negotiations
for a restructuring.
Turnover improved to Pounds 45.2m (Pounds 22.8m). Interest charges fell to
Pounds 4.96m (Pounds 5.39m) as property disposals allowed the group to repay
Pounds 17.8m of borrowings.
Losses per share were cut to 15.4p (31.9p).
